collection_description: IKONIKS live on the blockchain & travel between the wallets of Iconic Collectors. New sets of IKONIKS will be released in limited edition drops, showcasing 3D Animated portrayals of the most iconic people in human history. Inspired by the likes of Influencers, World Leaders, Actors, Musicians, Athletes, Entrepreneurs & more All IKONIKS are uniquely handmade & comes with a link to the Golden Membership Club Card. The Golden Membership Card will grant you access into the IKONIKS Club, which will act as your proof of membership for all future Exclusive Drops, Airdrops, Metaverse Nightclub Events, Giveaways, Merchandise & more! After completing the final drop of IKONIKS collectible figures we will build & host Nightclub Events in the Decentraland Metaverse on purchased Estate. All owners of IKONIKS NFTs will co-own the Nightclub & earn Ethereum by promoting events & selling tables, with proceeds sent directly to the wallets. "Icons are not born - they are created"
